Placeholder Recurring Encounter

Something happens! In the swamp. It's a big place.

choices:

* Negotiate = Try to convince them
    @if check negotiation easy {
      You convince them!
      +heal_spirits small
    } @else {
      You fail!
      +rem_gold small
    }
  
* Fight = Do the ultimate punchies
    @if check combat trivial {
        You win!
        +heal_spirits small
    } @else {
        You lose!
        +damage_health trivial
        +damage_spirits trivial
    }

* Sneak = Use big sneaky skills
    @if check cunning trivial {
        You win!
        +heal_spirits small
    } @else {
        You lose!
        +damage_health trivial
        +damage_spirits trivial
    }

